description:
Though parameters of this api are 'updated_since' , 'project_id' and 'deleted',
the error message is "Only 'updated_since' and 'project_id' are understood."
It shoud be "Only 'updated_since', 'project_id' and 'deleted' are understood."
title: error message of os-cells sync_instances api is incorrect
